INSTALLATION

     To install 'criticism' with C<make> give the following 
     commands to your favorite shell:

         tar -zxf criticism-1.02.tar.gz
         cd criticism-1.02
         perl Makefile.PL
         make
         make test
         make install 

     Or if you prefer C<Module::Build>, try this:

         tar -zxf criticism-1.02.tar.gz
         cd criticism-1.02
         perl Build.pl
         ./Build
         ./Build test
         ./Build install 
